      Classes in com.k2.Expressions.evaluators that implement Evaluator 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  GenericEvaluator<E>
      The generic evaluator provides an implementation of the GetterEvaluator interface.
      class  ObjectOrParameterEvaluator<E>
      This class extends the generic evaluator and allows the values returned for parameter expressions to be fulfilled by values from the generic evaluators value source and the values set on the evaluator.
      class  ParamterOrObjectEvaluator<E>
      This class extends the generic evaluator and allows the values returned for parameter expressions to be fulfilled by values from the generic evaluators value source and the values set on the evaluator.
      class  SimpleParameterEvaluator
      This class provides an implementation of the Evaluator interface and the ParameterEvaluator interface As such it is capable of providing values for parameter expressions
